Dr. Foster Cline.</p><h3>Parents will learn how to:</h3><ul><li>Handle Misbehavior Without Breaking a Sweat</li><li>Neutralize Arguments&hellip;.Every time</li><li>Teach Kids to Listen&hellip;the First Time</li><li>Avoid Power Struggles</li><li>Manage Whining and Complaining</li><li>Know What to do When Your Kids Leave You Speechless</li><li>Build Cooperation with School People</li><li>Turn Your Words into Gold</li></ul><h5>Class size is limited. Pre-registration is required.</h5><p><a href="https://secure.accessacs.com/access/eventlogin.aspx?id=OvlE0wQ21wj2NYUAxCycwg==&amp;site=1233&amp;ReturnUrl=events%2fwz_people.aspx&amp;ChurchID=3183&amp;EventID=50614&amp;sn=1233" class="button">Register</a></p><hr><h3><img src="http://www.pcctoday.com/monkimage.php?mediaDirectory=mediafiles&amp;mediaId=1774609&amp;fileName=graphic--photo--amy-slater-0-0-112-168.jpg" width="112" height="168" alt="GRAPHIC : photo : Amy Slater" title="GRAPHIC : photo : Amy Slater" style="float: left; margin: 0px 20px 10px 0;">Instructor Info</h3><p class="class-intstructor-bio"><b>Amy Slater</b>&nbsp;is the Early Childhood Director at Portland Christian Center. She is also a certified Love &amp; Logic Instructor and has taught love and logic classes to over 200 couples. Amy applies Love &amp; Logic principles in her own family life with her husband and three children, ages 6, 8, and 10.&nbsp;</p><div class="clr">&nbsp;</div><p><a href="https://www.facebook.com/amy.hayburnslater" class="facebook">Facebook</a> <a a="" href="mailto:aslater@pcctoday.com" class="email">Email</a>&nbsp;</p>